It also says: The **Upper Corpse** is **Peng Shan**, making **people crave rich flavors**, their **desires congealing and stagnant**;
The **Middle Corpse** is **Peng Zhi**, making **people covet wealth and treasures**, **fond of anger and wrath**;
The **Lower Corpse** is **Peng Jiao**, making **people love fine clothing**, **indulging in young women’s** **charms**.
Also named the **Three Poisons**.
